node.text: Try saying “popper pretzel” five times fast! Yeah, we know it’s a mouthful, just like this zesty ring. Use store-bought pizza dough to make pretzel bites stuffed with cheesy jalapeños, then serve with a creamy cilantro lime dip to tame the spice. This appetiser is a championship ring you’re guaranteed to win on your next game day. Link in bio!!
